data.description: Welcome to your home situated on cul-de-sac street in the Via Renata section of the Master Planned Community of Lakes of Bella Terra conveniently located off of Westpark Tollway in Richmond, TX! Your K. Hovnanian Home offers granite counters in the kitchen, 5 spacious bedrooms, large living area with gas fireplace, covered back patio, and large backyard! Lakes of Bella Terra boasts plentiful amenities to meet your family's needs including Catch & Release Ponds, Walking Trails, Fitness Gym, Volley Ball Court, Tennis Courts, Swimming Pools, a Dog Park, and schools all conveniently located inside this Master Planned Community!
